OL,3,CFamily cat crushed as tree smashes
OL,4,Cthrough houses during Storm Dave
OL,6,FA family cat has been crushed to death
OL,7,Fafter a tree fell onto two houses in
OL,8,FStaffordshire, during Storm Dave's
OL,9,Fstrong winds.
OL,11,FThe tree fell on properties on Windsor
OL,12,FCrescent in Kinver over the weekend.
OL,14,FIt's left a huge hole in the roof of
OL,15,Fboth semi-detached houses, and cars
OL,16,Fhave also been completely crushed.
OL,18,FOne of the families told ITV News
OL,19,FCentral they are having to stay with
OL,20,Floved ones while they assess the
OL,21,Fdamage to their home.
