OL,3,CFamily cat crushed as tree smashes
OL,4,Cthrough houses during Storm Dave
OL,6,F"He was the best cat"
OL,8,FThe family, who are staying with loved
OL,9,Fones, paid tribute to their cat
OL,10,FMarshall.
OL,12,FThey said he was "the best cat", one
OL,13,Fwho was "really friendly".
OL,15,FThey added that Marshall used to
OL,16,F"greet all the neighbours" and was
OL,17,Freally just a "big fat thing".
