OL,3,CFamily cat crushed as tree smashes
OL,4,Cthrough houses during Storm Dave
OL,6,FResidents say they have repeatedly
OL,7,Fraised concerns for the state of the
OL,8,Ftree with South Staffordshire Council,
OL,9,Fbut say nothing's been done.
OL,11,FWe have contacted the council for a
OL,12,Fresponse.
